parameters.name: BX
parameters.description:
GSE X component of the magnetic-field component in nT.                  
      X points from Earth to the Sun.

parameters.name: BY
parameters.description:
GSE Y component of the magnetic field component in nT.                  
      Y is parallel to the ecliptic plane and perpendicular to the            
      Earth-Sun line, positive opposite to the direction of the Earth's       
      motion.

parameters.name: BZ
parameters.description:
GSE Z component of the magnetic field component in nT.                  
      Z is perpendicular to the ecliptic plane.
